          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character92223",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/0cb2c22c57b20b09c40fa1920dc5f30d_8717182059636274295.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The settlement of the tribe who live alongside the Yumkasaurs. Their ancestors suspended giant trees here with ropes and grappling hooks, hence the name, \"Scions of the Canopy.\"</p>",
                "key": "Canopy of the Clifftops"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character19929",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/a99f50c50f28fc22e4b0944073293147_5539324278146344723.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Long, long ago, there was an age when the earth refused to accept seeds, when flowers withered and people could no longer turn to the land for sustenance. Instead, the ancestors of that ancient era turned to the gods of night for guidance.</p>",
                "key": "Temple of Ancient Forebears"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character8921",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/02653b8c16262f58fb0cfce50bc449a6_2470839595165418823.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>A world born from wall graffiti, or one concealed by expressive writings... Who knows which of these it is?</p>",
                "key": "Where the Painted Realm Unfolds"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character24508",
                "img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/cf6c06420cae2c90e081a2b8b8f84964_6410457298383427717.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>\"O puny people, o power-hungry race — what price are you willing to pay? What sacrifice will you make for that which you covet?\"</p><p><br></p>",
                "key": "Venture to a Secret Isle"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
      ]
    },
